: null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my master, O Patron of the Age! May Allah’s blessings be upon you and upon your Household. Today is Friday, which is your day on which your advent is expected to bring about relief to the believers at your hands and killing of the disbelievers with your sword.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay mere maula ay Sahebaz Zamaan (a.t.f.s) aap par aur aap ke ahle khaana par Khuda ki rehmate’n naazil ho. Yeh roz'e Juma (Friday) aap ka din hai aur is mein mai aap ke zuhoor ki ummeed aur aap ke zariye momeneen ke liye raahat o itmenaan ki tawaqqo’n karta hu aur aap ki talwaar ke zariye na-farmano ke qatl ka ummeed waar hu.", "Urdu": "اے میرے آقا اے صاحب زماںؑ! آپ پر اور آپؑ کے اہلِ خاندانؑ پر خدا کی رحمتیں ہوں۔ یہ جمعہ کا دن ہے جوآپؑ کا دن ہے جس میں آپؑ کے ظہور اور آپؑ کے ذریعے مومنوں کی آسودگی کی توقع ہے اور آپ کی تلوار سے کافروں کے قتل کی امید ہے۔", "RArabic": "YAA MAWLAAYA YAA SAAHEBAZ ZAMAANE SALAWAATUL LAAHE ALAYKA WA A’LAA AALE BAYTEKA HAAZAA YAWMUL JOMO-A’TE WA HOWA YAWMOKAL MOTAWAQQAO’ FEEHE ZUHOOROKA WAL FARAJO FEEHE LIL MOMINEENA A’LAA YADAYKA WA QATLUL KAAFEREENA BE SAYFEKA.", "ArabicText1": "یَامَوْلَایَ یَاصَاحِبَ الزَّمَانِ صَلَوَاتُ اللہِ عَلَیْکَ وَعَلٰی آلِ بَیْتِکَ ھٰذَا یَوْمُ الْجُمُعَۃِ وَھُوَ یَوْمُکَ الْمُتَوَقَّعُ فِیْہِ ظُھُوْرُکَ وَالْفَرَجُ فِیْہِ لِلْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ عَلٰی یَدَیْکَ وَقَتْلُ الْکَافِرِیْنَ بِسَیْفِکَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010585, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "On this day, O my master, I am your guest and in your vicinity and you, my master, are generous and the descendant of the generous people, and you are commanded to receive your guests and neighbors hospitably; so, receive me as your guest and neighbor. May Allah’s blessings be upon you and upon your Household, the immaculate.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aur ay mere aaqa mai is din aap ka mehmaan hu aur aap ke zer'e saaya hu. Ay karim aaqa aap karim logo’n ki aulaad mein se hai aur aap (Allah ki jaanib se) ziyaafat aur panah par maamur hai. Pas aap meri ziyaafat farmaaiye aur mujhe panah dijiye. Aap par aur aap ke paakeeza ahle khaana par Allah ki rehmate’n naazil ho.", "Urdu": "اور اےمیرے آقا میں آج کے دن آپ کی پناہ میں ہوں اور اے میرے آقا آپ کریم اور کریموں کی اولاد سے ہیں اور مہمان رکھنے اور پناہ دینے پر مامور ہیں اب مجھے مہمان کیجیے اور پنا ہ دیجئے اور آپ کے پاک و پاکیز ہ اہلِ خاندان پرخدا تعالیٰ کی رحمتیں ہوں۔", "RArabic": "WA ANAA YAA MAWLAAYA FEEHE ZAYFOKA WA JAAROKA WA ANTA YAA MAWLAAYA KAREEMUN MIN AWLAADIL KERAAME WA MAAMOORUN BIZ-ZEYAAFATE WAL EJAARATE FA-AZIFNEE WA AJIRNEE SALAWAATUL LAAHE A’LAYKA WA A’LAA AHLE BAYTEKAT TAAHEREENA.", "ArabicText1": "وَاَنَا یَامَوْلَایَ فِیْہٖ ضَیْفُکَ وَجَارُکَ وَاَنْتَ یَامَوْلَایَ کَرِیْمٌ مِّنْ اَوْلَادِ الْکِرَامِ وَمَامُوْرٌۢ بِالضِّیَافَۃِ وَالْاِجَارِۃِ فَاَضِفْنِیْ وَاَجِرْنِیْ صَلَوَاتُ اللہِ عَلَیْکَ وَعَلٰی اَھْلِ بَیْتِکَ الطِّیِّبِیْنَ الطَّاھِرِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 2, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Allah’s (s.w.t) choicest blessings be upon Mohammed and his holy progeny.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Parwardigaar Tu rehmat naazil farma Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unki Aal (a.s) par.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! رحمت نازل فرما حضرت محمدؐ اور انکی آل ؑپر۔", "RArabic": "ALLAHUMMA SWALLE ALAA MUHAMMADIW WA AALE MUHAMMADIN", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّ